// Special Notes
- Project emphasizes the single outlet principle for managing multiple modes
- Documentation is written in Chinese (中文)
- Focus on practical examples and best practices
- Maintain clear separation between Tailwind CSS and CSS variable modes
- Plugin UI supports both English and Chinese languages
